These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, chess, drawing, reading
4 different games are played: canasta, backgammon, scrabble, go
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is between the person playing scrabble and the person playing backgammon##2
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left or right of the person playing scrabble##3
3. the person playing scrabble is not to the left of the person playing scrabble##8
4. the person playing backgammon is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
6. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the person playing canasta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | reading  | camping | drawing | chess  |
| Game   | canasta | scrabble   | go  | backgammon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
House: art-deco, craftsman, modern, gothic-revival
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, journalist, nurse, project-manager
1. the project-manager is not to the left of the project-manager##8
2. the art-deco house is somewhere to the right of the gothic-revival house##5
3. the art-deco house is the journalist##1
4. the gothic-revival house is between the art-deco house and the craftsman house##2
5. the craftsman house is somewhere between the modern house and the designer##7
6. the nurse is somewhere to the left of the craftsman house##5
7. the designer is not to the left of the designer##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| House   | modern | craftsman          | gothic-revival | art-deco     |
| Job    | nurse      | project-manager | designer | journalist |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, chinese, thai, turkish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, family, superhero
1. the person watching adventure movies is not to the left of the thai##8
2. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1
3. the chinese is on the right of the indian##1
4. the chinese is in an even position##4
5. the turkish is on the far left or far right##3
6. the indian is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5
7. the turkish is the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality           | indian | chinese | thai     | turkish |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | superhero   | adventure | family    |

