.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, aquamarine, fuchsia, ebony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, cycling, handball, rugby
1. the person who likes ebony is somewhere between the person who likes blood-red and the person who likes aquamarine##7
2. the person who likes fuchsia is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
3. the person who likes ebony is somewhere between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes blood-red##7
4. the person who likes fuchsia is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
5. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who's sport is cycling##7
6. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who likes ebony##5
7. the person who's sport is cycling is not to the left of the person who likes blood-red##8
8. the person who's sport is cycling is on the left or right of the person who likes ebony##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | aquamarine   | fuchsia | ebony | blood-red    |
| Sport         | climbing | rugby   | handball   | cycling |

