.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, polish, mexican, russian
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, dubstep, indie, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of indie##1
2. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the left of the canadian##5
3. the mexican is on the right of the fan of indie##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the fan of indie##3
5. the canadian is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
6. the russian is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
7. the russian is the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Nationality          | russian | canadian | polish  | mexican |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep   | pop         | indie | ambient |

