.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, sprite, water
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, funk, soul, r&b
1. the fan of funk is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
2. the fan of r&b is somewhere between the person drinking water and the fan of soul##7
3. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the fan of classical##5
4. the fan of r&b is not to the left of the fan of classical##8
5. the fan of r&b is not to the left of the person drinking cola##8
6. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking sprite##3
7. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of soul##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | cola      | sprite | almond-milk | water   |
| Music-Genre      | classical | soul | r&b  | funk |

