4. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere between the person watching animation movies and the dressmaker##7
5. the entrepreneur is not to the right of the project-manager##8
6. the project-manager is somewhere between the person watching animation movies and the entrepreneur##7

.:: Answer ::.
