.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, dubstep, indie, pop
There 4 different types of food: avocado, eggplant, peas, grapefruit
1. the fan of classical is between the fan of pop and the person eating avocado##2
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the far left##1
3. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
4. the fan of dubstep is somewhere to the right of the person eating avocado##5
5. the person eating eggplant is the person eating eggplant##1
6. the fan of indie is not the person eating peas##6
7. the fan of pop is not to the right of the fan of indie##8
8. the person eating avocado is not to the left of the person eating eggplant##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | classical | indie | dubstep |
| Food     | grapefruit | eggplant       | avocado  | peas    |

