.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, iced-tea, tea
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, motorbike, snowmobile, taxi
1. the person drinking tea is between the person driving the motorbike and the person driving the snowmobile##2
2. the person driving the airplane is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
3. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
4. the person drinking iced-tea is not to the right of the person drinking cola##8
5. the person driving the airplane is on the left or right of the person drinking cola##3
6. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person driving the airplane##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage         | iced-tea | cola      | tea   | soy-milk  |
| Transport   | taxi    | motorbike | airplane | snowmobile |

