.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: corn, lime, onion, pineapple
House: modern, futuristic, wooden, palace
1. the person eating onion is not to the right of the palace house##8
2. the modern house is not to the right of the person eating lime##8
3. the futuristic house is somewhere to the right of the person eating pineapple##5
4. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating onion is between the palace house and the wooden house##2
6. the person eating lime is on the far left##1
7. the person eating onion is on the left or right of the palace house##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | lime        | pineapple | onion      | corn    |
| House   | modern | wooden   | futuristic | palace |

