.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, dunhill, vegafina, montecristo
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, handball, ice-hockey, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##8
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not to the right of the cain-smoker##8
3. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
4. the cain-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
5. the montecristo-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the dunhill-smoker##7
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3
8. the montecristo-smoker is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Cigar   | montecristo | dunhill         | vegafina    | cain       |
| Sport      | handball | skateboarding | biathlon | ice-hockey |

