.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-14::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, rose, azalea, tulip
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, collecting, drawing, magic-tricks
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
2. the person who growstulip is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is somewhere to the right of the person who growstulip##5
4. the person who growsrose is between the person who growstulip and the person who's hobby is drawing##2
5. the person who growsiris is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2      |     3      |      4       |
| Flower   | iris     | rose | tulip        | azalea       |
| Hobby      | drawing | collecting  | card-games | magic-tricks |

