.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, papaya, watermelon, zucchini
4 different pets are kept: hamster, rabbit, goat, bird
 1. the owner of the bird is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goat##5
 2. the person eating zucchini is not to the left of the person eating watermelon##8
 3. the person eating grapefruit is the owner of the goat##1
 4. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
 5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 6. the owner of the rabbit is somewhere to the right of the person eating watermelon##5
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating grapefruit is not to the right of the owner of the goat##8
 9. the owner of the rabbit is not to the left of the person eating grapefruit##8
10. the person eating papaya is not to the left of the owner of the hamster##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | papaya    | watermelon | grapefruit | zucchini |
| Pet   | hamster | bird  | goat     | rabbit    |

