.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: asparagus, avocado, grapefruit, peas
4 different games are played: go, chess, canasta, snooker
1. the person eating grapefruit is the person playing go##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is not to the left of the person playing chess##8
3. the person playing chess is the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing snooker is the person eating peas##1
5. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
6. the person eating avocado is between the person playing chess and the person eating peas##2
7. the person eating grapefruit is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Food    | peas        | avocado | asparagus | grapefruit |
| Game   | snooker | canasta | chess   | go    |

