.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, fish, rabbit, snake
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, brazilian, german, argentine
1. the owner of the snake is not the german##6
2. the german is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the fish is somewhere between the owner of the rabbit and the owner of the snake##7
4. the brazilian is somewhere to the right of the owner of the cat##5
5. the brazilian is somewhere to the left of the argentine##5
6. the japanese is not to the right of the brazilian##8
7. the owner of the fish is not to the left of the argentine##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | cat  | snake | fish  | rabbit  |
| Nationality   | japanese | brazilian   | argentine | german |

