.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, frog, hamster, hedgehog
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, family, sports, thriller
1. the person watching family movies is not the owner of the chinchilla##6
2. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the left of the person watching thriller movies##8
4. the owner of the hamster is the person watching disaster movies##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is somewhere between the person watching family movies and the person watching disaster movies##7
6. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
7. the person watching sports movies is between the person watching thriller movies and the owner of the hamster##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | frog    | hedgehog | chinchilla | hamster |
| Movie-Genre   | family | thriller      | sports     | disaster     |

 